the little white house , in the warm springs historic district in warm springs , georgia , is the name of the personal retreat of u.s. president franklin d. roosevelt.http://www.gastateparks.org/littlewhitehouse he first came to warm springs for polio treatment , and liked the area so much that , as governor of new york , he had a home built on nearby pine mountain .

